## Description {#details}

Iterator over hash records producing symbol record offsets.

Abstracts away the fact that symbol record offsets on disk are off-by-one.

Definition at line 29 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/debuginfo/include/llvm/debuginfo/pdb/include/llvm/debuginfo/pdb/native/globalsstream-h">GlobalsStream.h</a>.
